{"TopicId":11187,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Inverse/Reverse Planes","CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-22T07:21:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-22T07:21:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI don\\\u0027t think this has been done yet, or if it has, at least hasn\\\u0027t been published.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027d like to share two designs I created tonight at 2 AM\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe first I call Inverse, because I inversed all of its wings and control surfaces - even landing gear - 180 degrees.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELook at this beautiful thing:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/JzDs6.png\u0022 alt=\u0022JzDs6.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt flies!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/9yoMah.png\u0022 alt=\u00229yoMah.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E... it spins!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dS7Ksh.png\u0022 alt=\u0022dS7Ksh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E... nevermind\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/hdUgjh.png\u0022 alt=\u0022hdUgjh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe next I call Reverse, because \u003Cem\u003Eeverything\u003C/em\u003E is backwards. It doesn\\\u0027t even face the runway. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt flies!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/lyiEch.png\u0022 alt=\u0022lyiEch.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...nevermind\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ieAE3h.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ieAE3h.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMy challenge to you (this is a challenge thread too, yay) is to actually fly these planes... anywhere. And land them again. Total distance travelled must be over 2 km. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EInverse will do that death roll if you leave SAS on while it\\\u0027s in air, but if you turn SAS off you will break your engine off lifting off the pad (turn is too sharp or something). \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EReverse... I don\\\u0027t know. Nothing I tried could get it out of its... brick fall. \u003Cstrong\u003ENOTE\u003C/strong\u003E: All controls are also reversed. If you want to turn left, try to turn right. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMinor modifications like more or less control surfaces are okay, but make sure they\\\u0027re inverse \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOtherwise use provided .crafts if you want to try this \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ascensiam","CreatedById":12621,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-22T12:33:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou\\\u0027re insane for treating your kerbals like this and you should feel bad. Let me give it a try. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"popeter123","CreatedById":18410,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-22T18:52:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eyou mean foward swept wings?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kymlaar","CreatedById":24642,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-22T19:49:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI accept this challenge! Having to land without SAS on something that wants to roll constantly and without a joystick sounds like a joy. I\\\u0027ll check back later tonight with an update. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-05-24T02:01:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAny success stories? Tears of frustration? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T07:51:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOne last bump. If nobody replies, I\\\u0027ll assume you\\\u0027re defeated by the challenge of flying these \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003Ecomplete failures\u003C/span\u003E marvels of engineering.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T07:54:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/JzDs6.png\u0022 alt=\u0022JzDs6.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://deseng.ryerson.ca/w/pub/Design/WebImages/SU47ForwardSweepWing.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022SU47ForwardSweepWing.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...More or less.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T09:34:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027d be ashamed if I called it an SU-47 attempt. No, somepony else has already done that, and it wasn\\\u0027t my objective.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StelarCF","CreatedById":13985,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T11:28:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cardgame\u0022 data-cite=\u0022cardgame\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027d be ashamed if I called it an SU-47 attempt. No, somebody else has already done that, and it wasn\\\u0027t 